name: Photography And Landscapes
description:
Trained on multiple stock images, as well as our own photography taken with a NIKON DSLR, and some other cameras as well as iphone and samsung shots.

GREAT FOR VIDEO GAME CONCEPT use, will never replace the joy of the real thing LOL.

phtdzk1 (use that on your prompt)
